package a37Abstract_Class;

public class aSample {
	
	/*
	 1. What is an abstract class?
	 * An "abstract class" is a class which can containthe abstract methods and is defined with the
	   keyword abstract.
	 * interface lo complete ga abstract methods untai classess lo vatiki complete implentation untadi.
	 * aa madhya lo layer a abstract class.
	 */
	
	/*
	 * Interface lo ani  100% abstract methods untai manam default ga echina tisukuntundi.
	 * normal class lo abstract methods petaleamu.
	 * abstract class lo non-abstract methods undochu undakapovachu and abstract methods petalantea
	   kachitam ga class kuda abstract ie undali.
	 */

}
